text:
<HistoricalDocument xmlns="http://example.com/historicaldocument">
  <Metadata>
    <Language>German</Language>
    <WritingDirection>ltr</WritingDirection>
    <PhysicalDescription>Parchment, 1 folio, good condition.</PhysicalDescription>
    <Description>Record concerning regulations for the city of Bern, specifically regarding tolls (pfiffer) and the conduct of officials.</Description>
    <Script>Latin</Script>
  </Metadata>
  <Page>
    <Header>
      <PageNumber>69</PageNumber>
    </Header>
    <Body>
      <Paragraph>
        <Line><Initial type="simple">D</Initial>arnach komē ir pfiffer vñ</Line>
        <Line>trumeter zuͦ minem herˀn uff</Line>
        <Line>die gallen vnd hofierten do</Line>
        <Line>sinen gnedigen des glich komē</Line>
        <Line>die windeschen pfiffer vnd</Line>
        <Line>trumeter vnd boͤggenslaher</Line>
        <Line>vñ hofierten do och nach irē</Line>
        <Line>sitten also ward minē gnedige</Line>
        <Line>herˀn vnd allen den sinē vil</Line>
        <Line>ereÿ erbotten Jt̄ morudes ge</Line>
        <Line>gen tag fürent wir do dannē</Line>
        <Line>vnd komen uff fritag nach sant</Line>
        <Line>Urbans tag der do wz der erst</Line>
        <Line>tag im brachmonet gonkurfen</Line>
        <Line>Dz ist ein schone stat mit zwey</Line>
        <Line>herlichen velshwesern ob der</Line>
        <Line>stat vñ uff sunitag darnach</Line>
        <Line>füren wir da dannē vñ uff</Line>
        <Line>zinstag vor sant Vitz tag</Line>
        <Line>komen zuͦ vns im gallen by xx</Line>
      </Paragraph>
      <MarginalNote placement="right_margin">
        <Line>Honores</Line>
        <Line>Marchio</Line>
        <Line>in exi</Line>
        <Line>biti.</Line>
      </MarginalNote>
    </Body>
  </Page>
</HistoricalDocument>
